    "body": "We can specify an exact compiler version in `truffle.js` file, as doc mentioned https://www.trufflesuite.com/docs/truffle/reference/configuration#compiler-configuration\r\n\r\n```\r\nmodule.exports = {\r\n  compilers: {\r\n    solc: {\r\n      version: \"^0.6.0\"\r\n    }\r\n  },\r\n\r\n  networks: {\r\n    development: {\r\n      host: \"127.0.0.1\",\r\n      port: 8545,\r\n      network_id: \"*\" // Match any network id\r\n    }\r\n  }\r\n};\r\n```\r\nThis is my `truffle.js` configuration.",
